data.description: This beautiful ranch home is just outside Maryville City limits and close to town! Offering a level corner lot, a 3br/2ba split bedroom plan with a spacious living area, and a wood burning fireplace. The master bedroom offers a newly tiled walk-in master shower. The eat-in kitchen offers stainless appliances, a backsplash, and a breakfast bar. The recently painted wood deck is great for entertaining and also has a fenced in yard! Call today to schedule a tour.
